author: ANDREW DALTON, KRISTIN M. HALL
title: Kris Kristofferson, singer-songwriter and actor, dies at 88 - The Associated Press
description: Kris Kristofferson, a Rhodes scholar who became a superstar songwriter, singer and actor, has died. A family spokeswoman says Kristofferson died at his home in Hawaii on Saturday. He was 88.

author: Scott Pianowski
title: Week 4 Booms and Busts: Castoff QBs provide plenty of fantasy football fireworks - Yahoo Sports
description: Scott Pianowski breaks down Sunday's fantasy highs and lows, including a trio of QBs producing a surprising amount of points.
